
## **HOW TO UPLOAD TO GITHUB**

### **Step 1: Create GitHub Repository**
1. Go to https://github.com
2. Click "New repository"
3. Name: `ghana-school-mis`
4. Description: "Ghana Senior High School Management Information System"
5. Choose: Public or Private
6. Don't initialize with README (we'll add ours)

### **Step 2: Prepare Your Files**
Create a folder on your computer and copy all the above files into their respective directories.

### **Step 3: Initialize Git Repository**
```bash
# Navigate to your project folder
cd ghana-school-mis

# Initialize git
git init

# Add all files
git add .

# Commit files
git commit -m "Initial commit: Complete Ghana School MIS with all features"

# Add remote repository
git remote add origin https://github.com/yourusername/ghana-school-mis.git

# Push to GitHub
git branch -M main
git push -u origin main
